metadata.name: Plastic Dissection - 5
metadata.description:
BY THE POWER OF GRAYSKULL!
Plastic Dissection series continue with one of my favorite characters growing up, the one and only Price Adam / He-man!
This toy series had a massive impact on my growing up. It fuelled me with all the inspiration I needed as a kid. One could almost say, I HAVE THE POWER! :D
1/1 NFT, for all the kid at heart adults out there.
